thread.title: James Rodgers
thread.title_full: Omega Rental Cars reviewed by James Rodgers

author: James Rodgers
title: James Rodgers
text: The vehicle was clean and ready to drive away with a full tank of fuel. It performed better than we had expected, especially for the rental price we paid. The staff were more than helpful when we returned the vehicle to the depot. We would definitely rent a vehicle again from Omega Rental Cars when we come back to New Zealand.
